{
  "stem": "5371.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had-- I had a paper, you know, but after a while, the SS guards in the women's camp knew me already, because we were coming in and out every day.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to come in several times, either to go for tools or lunchtime we had to bring in for the people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the other, if they're-- we are divided-- we're actually about 25.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are divided like in four or five people in each camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to bring in food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some-- some of the people from one of the group had to bring in food, soup for the people in the other camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I also had an opportunity to take some people who had, for instance, a sister or a mother in camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was able to take them in with me to see their sister, or mother, or brother, whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we had a-- a-- a magazine outside the camp, and we used to go in there several times a day to pick up different tools.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I told them if they worked in the area, in the-- in the area-- in the vicinity, I told them-- and they told me previously that I should look for so and so.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if I find them to let them know that they're-- they're alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I took them back and they met, which was a big thing, because you couldn't go-- a man could not go into-- to a woman's camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you even saw-- if an SS woman saw you talking to a woman, you were with a-- with a whip, she whipped you very badly.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got whipped a few times already from a-- until they got to know me.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
